attractive targets for <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX> or <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> with malicious
intentions, such as committing fraud for personal gain or
sabotaging federal <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">operations</ENAMEX>. Several <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">agencies</ENAMEX> have experienced
intrusions into their systems, and there are indications, such as
tests at the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Department of Defense</ENAMEX>, that the number of attacks is
growing and that many attacks are not detected.
